OL,3,CEx-policeman who took selfies at scene
OL,4,Cof teen's death cleared of misconduct
OL,6,FA former police officer who took
OL,7,Fselfies at the scene of a teenager's
OL,8,Fdeath is not guilty of misconduct in a
OL,9,Fpublic office, a judge has ruled.
OL,11,FRyan Connolly, 41, was cleared of four
OL,12,Fcharges after Recorder of Manchester
OL,13,FJudge Nicholas Dean KC discharged the
OL,14,Fjury part way through a trial at
OL,15,FManchester Crown Court.
OL,17,FJudge Dean ruled the prosecution's
OL,18,Fevidence could not amount to proving
OL,19,FConnolly committed misconduct and it
OL,20,Fwould not be legal for a jury to
OL,21,Fconsider verdicts on the charges.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773061885
OL,3,CEx-policeman who took selfies at scene
OL,4,Cof teen's death cleared of misconduct
OL,6,FHe told the court: "My conclusion is
OL,7,Fthe Crown cannot demonstrate the
OL,8,Fserious misconduct here, that the
OL,9,Fevidence is incapable of demonstrating
OL,10,Fserious misconduct, so the jury could
OL,11,Fnot reach a conclusion so that Mr
OL,12,FConnolly was guilty of misconduct in a
OL,13,Fpublic office."
OL,15,FHe ordered not guilty verdicts to be
OL,16,Frecorded on Friday, on the fifth day
OL,17,Fof the trial which began on Monday.
OL,19,FProsecutors have until Monday to
OL,20,Fconsider whether to appeal against the
OL,21,Fruling.
OL,26,@nD@TOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
