PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773061885
OL,3,CEx-policeman who took selfies at scene
OL,4,Cof teen's death cleared of misconduct
OL,6,FJurors had heard that Connolly, a
OL,7,FConstable with Merseyside Police, took
OL,8,Fselfies, including one lying on the
OL,9,Fgrass, when he was deployed to guard a
OL,10,Fcordon after 16-year-old Daniel Gee-
OL,11,FJamieson was killed in Belle Vale,
OL,12,FLiverpool, in 2018.
OL,14,FMore than 50 photos, including
OL,15,Fpictures of vulnerable people detained
OL,16,Fat hospitals as well as images of
OL,17,Fforce systems and Connolly's
OL,18,Fcolleagues, were found in the sent
OL,19,Ffolder of WhatsApp on his personal
OL,20,Fphone when he was arrested in February
OL,21,F2020, the court heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773061885
OL,3,CEx-policeman who took selfies at scene
OL,4,Cof teen's death cleared of misconduct
OL,6,FOpening the trial on Tuesday, Peter
OL,7,FWilson, prosecuting, said: "The
OL,8,Fprosecution say he has wilfully
OL,9,Fmisconducted himself by taking
OL,10,Finappropriate photographs where, we
OL,11,Fsay, there is no professional need to
OL,12,Fdo so. He's then retained them and
OL,13,Fsent them on."
OL,15,FBut the court heard that with the
OL,16,Fexception of one photo, sent to a
OL,17,Fsupervising officer, there was no
OL,18,Fevidence of who Connolly sent the
OL,19,Fpictures to.
OL,26,@oD@\OUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
