PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773061885
OL,3,CEx-policeman who took selfies at scene
OL,4,Cof teen's death cleared of misconduct
OL,6,FNo messages accompanying the images
OL,7,Fhad been retrieved from the phone.
OL,9,FThe jury was told the defendant
OL,10,Fclaimed the images were taken for work
OL,11,Fpurposes, but the court heard they had
OL,12,Fnot been uploaded to police systems.
OL,14,FAt the hearing on Friday, a note from
OL,15,Fone juror had asked the court to
OL,16,Fexplain why the defendant had taken
OL,17,Fthe photos, adding: "What was he
OL,18,Fgetting out of it?"
OL,26,@yD@UOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
