FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773061885
OL,3,CEx-policeman who took selfies at scene
OL,4,Cof teen's death cleared of misconduct
OL,6,FJudge Dean told jurors that misconduct
OL,7,Fin a public office is one of the few
OL,8,Fremaining common law offences which is
OL,9,Fhard to define and is often a form of
OL,10,Fcorruption.
OL,12,FHe gave the example of police officers
OL,13,Fsometimes being prosecuted for tipping
OL,14,Foff criminals about police
OL,15,Finvestigations for money ` but nothing
OL,16,Flike that had been suggested in
OL,17,FConnolly's case.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773061885
OL,3,CEx-policeman who took selfies at scene
OL,4,Cof teen's death cleared of misconduct
OL,6,FHowever Connolly, from Huyton,
OL,7,FMerseyside, will be back at the same
OL,8,Fcourt on Monday to be sentenced for
OL,9,Fthree counts of possession of extreme
OL,10,Fpornographic images which he
OL,11,Fpreviously admitted.
OL,13,FHe was formally dismissed in 2021 by
OL,14,FMerseyside Police, who described his
OL,15,Fbehaviour as "deplorable".
OL,17,FA misconduct hearing was told other
OL,18,Fimages found on his phone were racist,
OL,19,Fhomophobic and mocked disabled people,
OL,20,Fand messages showed he socialised with
OL,21,Fa known criminal.
OL,26,@wD@NOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
